N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6155.1 - Purpose

State Regulations

In accordance with the provisions of chapter 50 of the Laws
of 1989 this Part will establish the policy for setting fees to be paid for
publications and other services provided by the Division of Criminal Justice

Services, Bureau of Prosecution Services. The actual fee structure will be
subject to approval by the Director of the New York State Division of the

Budget. Notes
